name: Aubegine
description:
100% raw silk large wrap 
Aubegine - navy blue/deep purple
180cm x 55cm, 71" x 22"

Each raw silk scarf has a delicate fringe, this is the same colour as the fibres weaving through the scarf.

The raw silk are a heavier weave than the fine silk and have individual variations in the thickness of the fibres and the fabric, characteristic of hand made garments.  

All scarves and wraps are dry clean only and very cool iron.
